2020 Mail-In Hub

On Election Night, this hub will have a dashboard of live Pennsylvania results, and how to reconcile live and mail-in results.

Until then, here’s the current mail-in data.

As of 2020-10-24 8:33:29, 1,455,353 ballots have been returned, and 1,445,561 are outstanding.

Mail-in data from data.pa.gov. (Updated 2020-10-24 08:33:29)
